Change in approach: in docs we edit regions *and* headers, not just
marked regions. Headers are always fair game - auto-fix statements. We always
add <a id="claim-foo"></a> just before Markdown header to ensure
the TYPE-ID links always work (update if not).
Call this update_headers (default true), not update.

